cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.HC, cs.SY, cs.LG. 

The film is about robots and their role in war, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The film also touches on the topic of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and human-robot interaction (cs.HC). The decision-making process of robots in war can also be seen as a control systems problem (cs.SY). Finally, the use of code to instruct robots on how to act in the film can be related to machine learning (cs.LG).
